Title: Shahnaz Husain Under Eye Serum(25 ml)
Description: Spending too much time in front of the computer, stress and poor skin nourishment can lead to dark circles under the eyes which come in the way of your beauty. Infused with a blend of natural ingredients such as Honey, Aloe Vera, Cucumber and Rose Extracts, this Shahnaz Husain Under Eye Serum revitalizes the skin under your eyes and gives you flawless complexion. With the Rose extract existent in this natural serum controlling the oil production of your skin, you eye contour will remain refreshed at all times. Besides, this Shahnaz Serum also lightens under eye dark circles and tones your skin to give you an even complexion. Show off your beautiful skin by using the Shahnaz Husain Under Eye Serum. Directions for Use Apply around the eyes. Massage gently till absorbed. Use regularly for best results.
